Name Gloss Group
Transcription
Description
Closest FrameNet Frame(s) Aggregate
Maps to IARPA Source Concept(s)
Other aliases
Comments A set of entities that are seen as related and/or similar in one or more respects. Prototypically, these entities are the same 'kind' of thing and are spatially proximate to one another. Different metaphorical construals of groups are possible, involving Posssession, Containment, and/or PartWhole strucutre.
